				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is a pretty awsome spell. Good way for a enchanter to be able to solo. Just root the monster after letting it take one or 2 swings at you so your pet and beat up on it. cast Tashan on it. Root it. Then DoT it. Just dont do to much damage otherwise it will knock them out of root and you will have to re-root them. <BR>
<BR>
I found this spell in the cleric guild in Fel. I dont remember what the guys name was but he is on the right hand side of the guild when you walk into it. I think it cost 3pp and some gold i cant remember though. Well i hope i helped all you people who couldnt find the spell. :)<BR>
<BR>
Faldiari<BR>
enchanter of the 8th season<BR>

