<BR>
Yes Root is a good spell however it gets resisted a lot.<BR>
<BR>
Try this if things go bad.<BR>
<BR>
1. cast color flux (fast cast time, rarely resisted.<BR>
<BR>
2. cast mezmerize while the mob is stunned.<BR>
<BR>
3 THEN you cast gate of just flee to a zone.<BR>
<BR>
get your CHA up and this tactics works almost every time.(note I said almost)  hehe.<BR>
<BR>
